    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这两个加载器——Slowly Changing Data Loader和fast Changing Data Loader——它们的输入来源有什么区别吗？还是共享同样的上游？",
      "elements_involved": [
