      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，它们都接收Page Props、Page Settings和App Settings。但是slowly loader还多一个来源——系统参数和页面参数会先聚合成Page Props，然后再流入slowly。",
      "elements_involved": [
