    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把sysParams和params都连到pageProps，然后pageProps、pageSettings、appSettings三条线都指向slowly。接下来fast loader怎么连？",
